title: Canning Collection, 5 Books In 1, Canning Meat, Fish, Poultry, W
description:
Canning Collection, 5 Books In 1, Canning Meat, Fish, Poultry, Wild Game, Vegetables, Fruits, Pickles, Salsa(2014) - EPUB - zeke23
English | January 9th, 2014 | ASIN: B00GSZ7AEU | 212 Pages | EPUB | 0.24 MB
Covers a wide range of canning, from vegetables to meat. Guidelines that include prep of what you are canning and processing of the items. Very useful information. I have been canning for many years having learned from my Mother and Grandmother. I found this collection very useful.
I have been looking for a canning book like this, clear, easy to read, and to the point. Not fond of the kindle cloud reader. Hope I can get this in print version in the future.
I wish I had this book when I first started canning! More thorough than the Ball canning book. Not as many recipes but a lot more explanations and step by step guidance
